{"lemma":"سَكْرَةُ","slug":"سَكْرَةُ","root":"س.ك.ر","root_slug":"س-ك-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ك-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَكْرَة","root":"سكر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n20214","n20223","n20224"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of سَكِرَ (sakira), an occasion of drunkenness, a case of intoxication, an event of inebriety"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"alternative form of سُكَّار (sukkār, “bolt-lock”)","tags":["alt-of","alternative"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20214","headword_ar":"سكّرهُ","root":"skr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b2-  And see also 1, last two explanations. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukirato A^aboSaArunaA","text_ar":"سُكِرَتْ اَبْصَارُنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xv. 15], means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Our eyes have been prevented from seeing, and dazzled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have been covered over:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-' Amr Ibn-El-' Alà, S, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukirato","text_ar":"سُكِرَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", without teshdeed,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have been prevented from seeing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, K: *) or this latter, which is the reading of El-Hasan, means, accord. to him,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have been enchanted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or both mean,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have been covered"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1391},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and closed by enchantment, so that we imagined ourselves to behold things which we did not really see:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) Mujáhid explains the latter reading as meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have been stopped up;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have been covered by that which prevented their seeing, like as water is prevented from flowing by a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sikor","text_ar":"سِكْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dam"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A 'Obeyd:) and another reading is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakirato","text_ar":"سَكِرَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have become dazzled, like those of the intoxicated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh, Bd: *) AO says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboSaAru Alqawomi","text_ar":"اَبْصَارُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakirato","text_ar":"سَكِرَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people became affected by a giddiness; and an affection like cloudiness of the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakness of the sight, came over them, so that they did not see;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and Aboo-'Amr Ibn-El-'Alà says that this signification is derived from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukorN","text_ar":"سُكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as though their eyes were intoxicated: Zj says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayonuhu","text_ar":"عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakirato","text_ar":"سَكِرَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his eye became dazzled, and ceased to see."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suk~ira liloHaAjapi","text_ar":"سُكِّرَ لِلْحَاجَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opinion, was confused respecting the object of want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of a man only before he has determined upon the thing alluded to. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sk~rhu","text_ar":"سكّرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasokiyrN","text_ar":"تَسْكِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He squeezed his throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throttled him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaEiyru yusak~iru A=xara bi*iraAEihi Hat~aY yakaAdu yaqotuluhu","text_ar":"البَعِيرُ يُسَكِّرُ ا=خَرَ بِذِرَاعِهِ حَتَّى يَكَادُ يَقْتُلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camel throttles another with his arm so that he almost kills him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","T","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n20223","headword_ar":"سَكْرَةٌ","root":"skr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fit of intoxication:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakaraAtN","text_ar":"سَكَرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba bayona AlS~aHowapi","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ بَيْنَ الصَّحْوَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAls~akorapi","text_ar":"وَالسَّكْرَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away in state between that of sensibility and insensibility,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mental perception and inability thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fit of anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An overpowering sensation of delight, affecting youth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakorapu Almawoti","text_ar":"سَكْرَةُ المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The intoxication of death;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the confusion of the intellect by reason of the severity of the agony of death:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the oppressive sensation attendant upon death, which deprives the sufferer of reason:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in 1. 18:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oppressive sensation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and disturbance of the mind, and insensibility,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attendant upon death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, Mgh, K.) And in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sakorapu Alhami","text_ar":"سَكْرَةُ الهَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~awomi","text_ar":"النَّوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The oppressive sensation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attendant upon anxiety,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon sleep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Mgh","B","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n20224","headword_ar":"سَكَرَةٌ","root":"skr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayolamN","text_ar":"شَيْلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayolam","text_ar":"شَيْلَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuw^aAnN","text_ar":"زُوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"app. called by the former name because"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a decoction thereof is used as an anæsthetic;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said to be]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same that is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"murayoraA='u","text_ar":"مُرَيْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"often found"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in wheat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}